DB Schema

USER
id (PK)
unique_id
name
email (unique)
role (ADMIN / TEACHER / STUDENT)
is_status (boolean)


TEACHER_SUBJECT
id (PK)
teacher_id (FK → User.unique_id)
subject_id (FK → SUBJECT.id)


MARKS
id (PK)
student_id (FK → User.unique_id)
subject_id (FK → SUBJECT.id)
exam_type (IA1 / IA2 / IA3/Special)
marks
created_by_teacher_id (FK → User.unique_id)
marks_proof_pdf LONGBLOB


OTP_EVENTS
id (PK)
user_id (FK → USER.id)
otp_code
purpose (REGISTRATION / LOGIN / PASSWORD_RESET)
expiry_time
status (PENDING / VERIFIED / EXPIRED)
created_at

SUBJECT 
subject_name
semester
academic_year
